### Get all tournaments
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments

### Get one tournament
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments/4247976163262170

### Create tournament
POST http://localhost:3000/tournaments
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: admin

{
    "title": "Test Tournament",
    "description": "A test tournament",
    "date": "2026-05-01T10:00:00.000Z",
    "breaks": 10,
    "numberOfRounds": 3,
    "gameCategory": "69cd7f06a5fd0a6f13e52fde"
}

### Join tournament
POST http://localhost:3000/tournaments/4247976163262170/join
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: user

{
    "userId": "69cd7f06a5fd0a6f13e52fc0"
}

### TOURNAMENT FLOW - Follow steps 1-4 to test the full tournament lifecycle
### Step 1 - Knockout rounds
PUT http://localhost:3000/tournaments/4247976163262170/advancedRounds
X-User-Role: admin

### Step 2 - Check tournament to get the match IDs from rounds
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments/4247976163262170

### Step 3 - Record result for a match (use matchId from step 2)
PUT http://localhost:3000/matches/5281799122745019/record
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: user

{
    "winner": "69cd7f06a5fd0a6f13e52fb6",
    "outcome": "3-1"
}

### Step 4 - If only 1 match in last round, check if trophy was awarded to winner
GET http://localhost:3000/users/4888902451701504
